data.description: VRM sellers will entertain offers between $339,000 to $424,000.Welcome to 5528 Fairfield Place, a unique 4-bed, 2-bath home in a prestigious cul-de-sac. This residence blends a stunning location with captivating features. Meticulously landscaped surroundings and an irrigation system maintain the allure. The spacious 2-car garage and thoughtfully designed interior, including a master bedroom with a double vanity, offer comfort and convenience.The kitchen boasts custom-built stained cabinets and stone countertops, creating an open layout that connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen seamlessly. Additional features include a separate dining room, a charming sunroom, and an outdoor patio for entertaining.For versatility, the property offers a game room and workshop on the main floor and an upper level with an office, media room, and spacious bedroom. Ample attic space caters to storage needs. Recent updates bring a fresh and modern touch to this exceptional property. This home is a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and space, ready to welcome you. Don't miss the chance to make 5528 Fairfield Place your forever home—schedule a showing today and experience its unique charm!
